2. API REQUIREMENTS

This Software requires external API keys that you must obtain separately:
- DeepL API Key (Free or Pro tier from https://www.deepl.com/pro-api)
- Google Gemini API Key (from https://ai.google.dev/)

DeepL API usage:
- Both Free and Pro tiers: Unlimited translations through this Software
- Character limits are determined by your DeepL API plan

Google Gemini API usage:
- Governed by your Google API quota and billing settings

3. LICENSE TIERS

3.1 Free Tier
- Limited to 10 Gemini API calls per month (enforced by this Software)
- DeepL API: Unlimited calls (subject to your DeepL API plan limits)
- No technical support
- For evaluation and personal use

3.2 Pro Tier (Paid)
- Unlimited Gemini API calls (subject to your Google API quota)
- DeepL API: Unlimited calls (subject to your DeepL API plan limits)
- Priority technical support
- Commercial use allowed
- Requires valid license key from PIMCORE Store

